### Backup & Restore API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. List all backups
GET http://localhost:8080/api/backups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Get specific backup details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/backups/backup_2025-11-03_14-30-15_manual
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Create manual backup (return metadata only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/backups/create?returnFile=false&description=Test backup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Create manual backup and download ZIP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/backups/create?format=zip&description=Backup cu ZIP
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Create manual backup and download Excel
POST http://localhost:8080/api/backups/create?format=excel&description=Backup cu Excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Download backup as ZIP
GET http://localhost:8080/api/backups/backup_2025-11-03_14-30-15_manual/download/zip
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Download backup as Excel
GET http://localhost:8080/api/backups/backup_2025-11-03_14-30-15_manual/download/excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Restore from JSON backup (WARNING: Deletes all data!)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/backups/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backupName": "backup_2025-11-03_14-30-15_manual",
  "fromExcel": false
}

###

### 9. Restore from Excel backup (WARNING: Deletes all data!)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/backups/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backupName": "backup_2025-11-03_14-30-15_manual",
  "fromExcel": true
}

###

### 10. Delete backup
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/backups/backup_2025-11-03_14-30-15_manual
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

